  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "T7bvaYLpHWi2l/G7Zzs146TahLzluwYcBrew55/CBG4=",
    "originContent": "- Exchanges the authorization code for access + refresh tokens",
    "translatedContent": "- **トークンの有効期限切れ時に自動更新** — 手動再認証不要"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "JOHmNganoQMrjMdsCTkLkuxg6yyFokKZle2qjkJQb0s=",
    "originContent": "- **Auto-refreshes tokens** when they expire — no manual re-auth needed",
    "translatedContent": "- Anthropicリクエストに必要なAPIヘッダーを設定"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "6z6sFde9G6bFUhgNenqgfUErmf0QhZRxirSv8VPPzu0=",
    "originContent": "- Sets the required API headers on Anthropic requests",
    "translatedContent": "- **プロンプトキャッシュを保持**し効率的なトークン使用を実現"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
